Hospital.Schedules

Interface Schedulable

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    HasPreference
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BloodAnalyzer, Doctor, HospitalAdministrator, Machine, Nurse, Patient, Person, Staff, SurgicalEquipment, UltraSoundMachine, WarehouseManager, XRayMachine

    public interface Schedulable
    An interface for objects that can be scheduled, in other words, that can attend an appointment
